y":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"出嚟啦 ~  神探 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30b981d2c6e4e8959c42620a56a462ec2c5ced7","tid":242464,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:41:58.000Z","msg":"港鐵縱火：疑犯今晨因器官衰竭不治<br />\n05月14日(日) 09:31<br />\n<br />\n港鐵尖沙咀站列車今年2月發生有史以來最恐怖縱火案，造成19人受傷。消息指，案中被控有意圖縱火的被告張錦輝（60歲）留醫3個月後，今日清晨5時許於沙田威爾斯親王醫院，因器官衰竭不治。<br />\n<br />\n案發於今年2月10日晚上7時許，一列荃灣線列車由金鐘駛往尖沙咀途中，當時車廂逼滿乘客，在首卡車廂內的一名姓張（60歲）男子，突然取出一個酒樽，向自己下半身淋潑懷疑天拿水，繼而點着變火人，並在人群中亂衝，站在其周圍的多名乘客被波及，衣服沾染易燃液及起火燃燒，造成19人受傷，警方其後將張拘捕。"},{"pid":"664bb69ef90ac8f58057e66e57d5e49fe4a43226","tid":242464,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵縱火：疑犯今晨因器官衰竭不治<br />\n05月14日(日) 09:31<br />\n<br />\n港鐵尖沙咀站列車今年2月發生有史以來最恐怖縱火案，造成19人受傷。消息指，案中被控有意圖縱火的被告張錦輝（60歲）留醫3個月後，今日清晨5時許於沙田威爾斯親王醫院，因器官衰竭不治。<br />\n<br />\n案發於今年2月10日晚上7時許，一列荃灣線列車由金鐘駛往尖沙咀途中，當時車廂逼滿乘客，在首卡車廂內的一名姓張（60歲）男子，突然取出一個酒樽，向自己下半身淋潑懷疑天拿水，繼而點着變火人，並在人群中亂衝，站在其周圍的多名乘客被波及，衣服沾染易燃液及起火燃燒，造成19人受傷，警方其後將張拘捕。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170514/bkn-20170514093153241-0514_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170514%2Fbkn-20170514093153241-0514_00822_001.html&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2BzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=be59ac4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170514/bkn-20170514093153241-0514_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2e639aad466b83ffe816618bf7f910f77eedb25a","tid":242464,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"嘩訓成3個月"},{"pid":"b49f24bb02c4b3644e00e86698bad43fbf38c56b","tid":242464,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"Rip 香港真英雄"},{"pid":"3e8491fd79194a262f89cce162747c8e8f787100","tid":242464,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪因為燒傷令到細菌感染，導致器官衰竭？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其中一個原因啦<br />\n另外燒傷亦可以導致水份大量流失<br />\n<br />\n而最重要既，應該係大面積燒傷後引發發炎反應，發炎因子風暴令各個器官shut down，引起衰竭<br />\n<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"8959f1c907c4f87ecd9370f33f8ad6651a15a20c","tid":242464,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"燒傷女學生近況如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"6b859706008e0d1f6ba977eaad79517b9015fc8b","tid":242464,"uid":3842,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩訓成3個月</blockquote><br />\n浪費資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad63b75b01658934cc7f2f29208f92d7bf41a7d","tid":242464,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩訓成3個月</blockquote><br />\n希望佢有屋企人 我唔想找佢數"},{"pid":"3a1528cdb185738504af588dc6b28ef164d26cb5","tid":242464,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"160dc2e1551bf28ca12550b33d0e184f2171d0f6","tid":242464,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Rip 香港真英雄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靈堂又放 浩氣長存 牌扁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a01b1ac051590073e230c84ef8d4e11dd6f50f3","tid":242464,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"點解冇呼籲捐贈？"},{"pid":"f1f35107911a5650e0d8150bc4a422c37ef89121","tid":242464,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回