忘<br />\nWhat the fuck?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc9b59f4c5017e51d4814649e6de2ab67731813","tid":242464,"uid":62421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"Rest in pieces <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49b8e5fc403e70741c83bc12c656369a7817957","tid":242464,"uid":35266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果佢有得接受器管移植，香港人會唔會屌晒鬼？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個就係道德問題<br />\n到底疑犯值唔值得救?<br />\n甚至殺人犯喺有限資源上係唔係無權得到治療<br />\n<br />\n可以開個topic傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 果個仲係叫疑犯，一日未審訊，一日你都要當佢係無罪<br />\n2. 刑罰應該係由法庭去裁決，唔可以由任何人去行私刑<br />\n<br />\n當然囚犯有冇獲得醫療既權利，呢樣我覺得有討論空間<br />\n現代社會成撚日講囚犯要有基本人權，我屌你啦，人身自由唔係基本人權呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：大愛撚，覺得點都要救左先"},{"pid":"81cb6e2a207ab3372edff86686fb08f406dae110","tid":242464,"uid":55908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"成班未審先判<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地疑犯黎咋"},{"pid":"da661086c0ffe23038f07138e891ecf4eabc1d0f","tid":242464,"uid":2126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"人都死左，連登仔毫無人性，正禽獸"},{"pid":"ad59eaa193f707c3c9ad5ab2380fd5ee17258051","tid":242464,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"個女學生依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3f27c79a5f657fdbc01bb2066635edf2feec60","tid":242464,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"一代梟雄黃土一坯。<br />\n人生在世，結局難以強求，順勢而行，全力以赴，享受過程就好。"},{"pid":"691a2ce14